HEADWORD: Expository
<hw>Ex*pos"i*to*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Pertaining to,
or containing, exposition; serving to explain; explanatory;
illustrative; exegetical.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A glossary or <qex>expository</qex> index to the poetical
writers.</q> <rj><qau>Johnson.</qau></rj></p>

